public enum SimObjectType
extends java.lang.Enum<SimObjectType>

The SimObjectType enumeration type is used with the SimConnect.requestDataOnSimObject(int, int, int, SimConnectPeriod, int, int, int, int) call to request information on specific or nearby objects.
